content: it is good that we can be more active from now on. the website is getting larger, the activities start again.
as most of you know, we will start tournament next thursday
those who signed up i remind:
please make sure you are available within 48 hours after next thursday
because this is the period when all games have to be started
failing to start game within that time will  result with loss
so, make sure you have time on friday or saturday
all you have to do during those two days is to open 10 games for your opponents
and that should take no more than 10 minutes of your time
if any problems, please contact referees
and please be careful while clicking any buttons
open 10, join 10, there will be 20 games per person
last tournament, some eager players clicked to join games which werent theirs
and we had to cancel those games
so, to avoid mess, please stay calm
and click on on games whi ch are for you

so, next thursday, after class, you go to web, read the instructions, and start games
if you see that the Tournament server's New Games are allows you to create new games, that means we are free to go
